ation oregon shakespeare festival providence hospital foundation rogue valley medical center foundation st marys high school united way of jackson county and the university of oregon awards time magazine quality dealer award for oregon sports illustrated allstar dealer award presidents medal southern oregon university various medford and ashland chamber of commerce awards dealership awards include honda dealer awards chrysler corporation star dealer awards toyotas presidents awards and the coveted porsche premier dealer award education stanford university university of oregon lithia chrysler dodge jeep  vista street ashland or wwwlithiacom franchises chrysler dodge jeep ram committees  legislative affairs regulatory affairs nada foundation ambassador of distinction deac member for  years previous ataenada dealership operations government relations industry relations policy and bylaws public affairs strategic planning task force inside this section more about nada the nada story  the nada story began in  when  auto dealers traveled to the nation’s capital to convince congress not to impose a luxury tax on the automobile they successfully argued that the automobile is a necessity of american life not a luxury from that experience nada was born today nada represents nearly  newcar and truck dealers with  franchises both domestic and international mission statement  the purpose of the national automobile dealers association is to serve and represent the franchised newcar and truck dealers of america their management and employees nada has two main goals  to promote and enhance the franchise system and effectively communicate dealer views and concerns to all branches of the federal government to manufacturers and the public and  to strengthen the financial position of members as retailers through professional programs and services that improve the business skills of management personnel and the technical capabilities of nonmanagement employees deboer sidney b  the wall street transcript sidney b deboer sidney b deboer is the chairman and chief executive officer of lithia motors inc his professional background began in  working for his father as an office manager in an automobile dealership from  to  he sold cars afterwards he became a dodge dealer in ashland oregon and has been managing dealerships ever since mr deboer attended the university of oregon where he studied business education and the university of oregon where he majored in accounting from  to  he has received numerous awards the latest being ‘time magazine quality dealer award’ in  his professional memberships include american import automotive dealers association chrysler dealer council honda dealer council medford new car dealers association national auto dealers association oregon auto dealers association and toyota dealers council related interviewssidney b deboer  lithia motors incjune   cartlatest newsjames abate of centre asset management sees consumer demand driving new stock highsmalcolm e polley of stewart capital and how to play the health care stockstimothy biltz ceo of lumos networks identifies the key component for future g networksthe wall street transcript is a completely unique resource for investors and business researchersover  ceo equity analyst and money manager interviewssubscribe nowsign up for newsletter weekly email with new indepth interviews email most popular interviewsdelivering longterm results with a riskmanaged growth fundjames a abate published july   in investing strategiescompanies covered amat jnj coh rl cog nvda adbe atvi klac amzn nflx goog fb glw mu   wfm jwn cmg gps eqt rice spls buy finding investments with favorable risk and reward opportunitieshenry beukema published july   in investing strategiescompanies covered orcl msft nsrgy amzn wfm lrlcy agn lnr buy better returns and lower risk in the midcap spacemalcolm e polley published july   in investing strategiescompanies covered praa hurn fii fl nke amzn wfm wba rad buy most po